channel.title: SeaScape V3 { Recruiting }
channel.description:
Hi, I am not releasing this yet as it still needs some work. SeaScape source is funscap3 but i have put new places and things in so it doesn't seem like it was funscap3, so i call it Funscap3 Remix by Me (Bonzakid). SeaScape has new starting points, training spots aswell as Skillcapes and items from Silabsoft creations. I am currently looking for a hoster or 2 who can host it for me without me using Hamachi, also people can fill out this thing below to get a job, you can chose but some might be taken. I will PM you if you get the job, thanks.
Also feel free to visit our homewebsite at http://www.seascape.uni.cc or forums at http://seascape.smfforfree3.com
